      "pMessage": "How are you feeling?"
    },
    {
      "ID": 81,
      "pMessage": "It’s the start of a new\nadventure, eh?"
    },
    {
      "ID": 82,
      "pMessage": "Heh, you look as if you’re\nhaving a strange day."
    },
    {
      "ID": 83,
      "pMessage": "If you’re feeling unsure,\nask around. Some people\nhave good advice to offer."
    },
    {
      "ID": 84,
      "pMessage": "You look dog tired. It’s\nimportant to know when\nto rest."
    },
    {
      "ID": 85,
      "pMessage": "Even the harshest journeys\nhave a way of becoming\nfond memories."
    },
    {
      "ID": 86,
      "pMessage": "Come what may, your journey\nwon’t stop till you do."
    },
    {
      "ID": 87,
      "pMessage": "Excited by your first real\njourney? Good. There’s no\npoint if it stops being fun."
    },
    {
      "ID": 88,
      "pMessage": "How goes?"
    },
    {
      "ID": 89,
      "pMessage": "Head straight for your goal,\nor take a few detours on the\nway—it’s your journey."
    },
    {
      "ID": 90,
      "pMessage": "Up and down, sink or swim…\nThis place is a lot like life."
    },
    {
      "ID": 91,
      "pMessage": "Company on the road is a\nprecious thing. Treat your\nfriends well."
    },
    {
      "ID": 92,
      "pMessage": "It’s just as you catch your\nstride you’re most likely to\ntrip. Don’t get careless."
    },
    {
      "ID": 93,
      "pMessage": "It’s nearly the big moment,\neh?"
    },
    {
      "ID": 94,
      "pMessage": "I’m impressed you made it\nall the way out here."
    },
    {
      "ID": 95,
      "pMessage": "Sometimes the shortest way\nthere is the long way ’round."
    },
    {
      "ID": 96,
      "pMessage": "You’ve come so far. Just a\nlittle further, now."
    },
    {
      "ID": 97,
      "pMessage": "Rough road, eh? You’re\nnearly to Florem, though."
    },
    {
      "ID": 98,
      "pMessage": "The same road looks pretty\ndifferent coming and going,\nhuh?"
    },
    {
      "ID": 99,
      "pMessage": "Just try to be careful.\nThat’s all I ask."
